  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8-\u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1-\u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd-\u0b89\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0b9f\u0bbf-\u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8/175-302613",
  "time_ut": 1660892413,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b89\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Immediate action on price increase",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Market, Commerce and Food Security Minister Nalin Fernando has said that while gas supply has now returned to normal, necessary measures will be taken to control the price.",
        "He mentioned that taking steps to control the price of gas by paying attention to the price of the world market, cost and the retail price of gas sold to consumers.",
        "At the same time, the concerned party has been informed to present a report to the Consumer Authority to examine whether the price increase of many domestic products including cement, iron, wire and biscuits are reasonable and about their price formula.",
        "According to the report, Minister Nalin Bandara said that immediate action will be taken to control their prices. (R)"
      ],
